iate%20in%20value%20or%20have%20little%20sentimental%20value.%20Think%3A%20a%20brand-new%20car%2C%20a%20designer%20handbag%2C%20or%20the%20latest%20tech%20gadget%20you%20%3Cem%3Ehad%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20have%2C%20but%20barely%20use%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20me%2C%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20splurges%20people%20regret%20that%20I%20come%20across%20would%20be%20buying%20new%20cars%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Brenton%20Harrison%2C%20CFP%C2%AE%20professional%20and%20financial%20advisor%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmoneynewproblems.com%2Fhome%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ENew%20Money%20New%20Problems%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BThe%20problem%20with%20it%20is%20you're%20never%20gonna%20get%20what%20you%20paid%20for%20a%20car%20back%20in%20return%2C%20so%20I%20come%20across%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20who%20end%20up%20regretting%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20smaller%20splurges%2C%20like%20late-night%20food%20delivery%20or%20clothing%20hauls%2C%20can%20pile%20up%20and%20leave%20people%20feeling%20unsatisfied.%20There%20comes%20a%20point%20where%20items%20feel%20more%20like%20useless%20clutter%20taking%20up%20space%20than%20meaningful%20additions%20to%20your%20everyday%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20get%20a%20dopamine%20hit%20when%20we%20experience%20something%20new%2C%20like%20when%20the%20package%20arrives%20and%20we%20use%20a%20new%20item%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20but%20then%20the%20dopamine%20wears%20off%2C%26quot%3B%20explains%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.joyinliving.life%2Fabout-me%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EJoy%20Slabaugh%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20CFP%C2%AE%20professional%2C%20financial%20therapist%2C%20and%20educator.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22182c5191-34cb-45e7-a085-7981f746a03b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESplurges%20that%20are%20worth%20your%20money%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20all%20splurges%20come%20with%20buyer's%20remorse%2C%20or%20a%20hefty%20price%20tag.%3C%