al%20retirement%20into%20the%20digital%20age%20and%20leaving%20behind%20one%20of%20the%20strangest%20government%20facilities%20still%20in%20operation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20major%20shift%20announced%20on%20Monday%2C%20the%20Office%20of%20Personnel%20Management%20(OPM)%20said%20that%20it%20will%20begin%20processing%20all%20new%20federal%20retirement%20applications%20digitally%20starting%20June%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPaper%20applications%20will%20no%20longer%20be%20accepted%20from%20July%2015%2C%20ending%20a%2050-year%20bureaucratic%20tradition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRetirement%20from%20federal%20service%20is%20finally%20entering%20the%20digital%20age%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20OPM%20interim%20director%20Chuck%20Ezell.%20He%20called%20the%20move%20a%20%26quot%3Btransformative%20step%20that%20honors%20the%20service%20of%20federal%20employees%26quot%3B%20with%20a%20retirement%20process%20%26quot%3Bworthy%20of%20the%2021st%20century.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20decades%2C%20the%20federal%20government%20has%20stored%20and%20processed%20retirement%20paperwork%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffederal-retirement-pennsylvania-mine-paperwork-doge-musk-crosshairs-real-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Econverted%20mine%20230%20feet%20below%20Boyers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Pennsylvania.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20more%20than%20400%20million%20records%20housed%20in%2026%2C000%20filing%20cabinets%2C%20the%20process%20was%20slow%2C%20manual%2C%20and%20reliant%20on%20the%20elevator's%20shaft%20%E2%80%94%20a%20system%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%20described%20as%20%26quot%3Binsane.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20elevator%20breaks%20down%20sometimes%2C%20and%20nobody%20can%20retire%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20said%20at%20a%20White%20House%20press%20conference%20in%20February.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%2C%20who%20leads%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http