0but%20a%20constitution%20can%20contain%20small%20things%20that%20demonstrate%20your%20family%20values.%20Mine%2C%20for%20example%2C%20dictates%20that%20we%20always%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairports-passengers-go-through-customs-before-arriving-in-the-us-list-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edrop%20off%20and%20pick%20up%20a%20family%20member%20traveling%3C%2Fa%3E%20through%20to%20the%20airport.%20It's%20a%20way%20to%20show%20we%20care%20and%20be%20of%20service%20to%20our%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20I'm%2067%20(or%2C%20as%20I%20like%20to%20say%2C%20Barry%20version%206.7)%2C%20and%20I%20work%20with%20affluent%20young%20people%20(ages%2014%20to%2030)%20on%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finterview-questions-ask-about-professional-development-2018-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epersonal%20and%20professional%20development%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20structure%20my%20approach%20around%20the%20seven%20pillars%2C%20but%20also%20believe%20there%20are%20specific%20lessons%20young%20people%20need%20to%20succeed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20five%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcollege-teacher-shares-kids-should-know-before-high-school-ends-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elessons%20every%20parent%20should%20teach%20their%20teens%3C%2Fa%3E%20before%20college.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227c66b2e2-8191-4037-8dae-0d36c4d75828%5C%22%3EGet%20outside%20your%20comfort%20zone%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20outside%20your%20comfort%20zone%20takes%20courage%2C%20and%20courage%20builds%20confidence.%20It's%20essential%20that%20young%20people%20have%20confidence%20in%20themselves%20personally%20and%20professionally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20every%20young%20person%20I%20work%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-make-a-vision-board-2016-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuild%20a%20vision%20board%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20collecting%2020%20images%20of%20things%20that%20will%20empower%20them.%20One%20of%20those%20things%20must%20be%20an%20impossible%20goal%20%E2%80%94%20something%20that%20seems%20so%20big%20it's%20hard%20to%20imagine.%20Just%20naming%20that%20goal%20is%20stepping%20out%20of%20the%20comfort%20zone%2C%20and%20it%20encourages%20big-picture%20thinking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20youth%20I%20work%20with%20keep%20their%20vision%20boards%20as%20the%20lockscreen%20on%20their%20phones.%20I%20do%20the%20same%20thing%20%E2%80%94%20my%20vision%20board%20has%20pictures%20related%20to%20books%2C%20fitness%2C%20unprocessed%20foods%2C%20and%20discipline.%20I'm%20reminded%20of%20my%20goals%20every%20time%20I%20look%20at%20my%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2235780d69-fc35-4e31-a722-efdecf713b31%5C%22%3EPractice%20going%20first%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFuture%20leaders%20need%20to%20be%20comfortable%2C%20well%2C%20leading.%20So%2C%20I%20encourage%20people%20to%20practice%20that%20on%20the%20micro%20level%20by%20going%20first%20whenever%20they%20can.%20Teach%20your%20teens%20to%20initiate%20things%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20it's%20a%20handshake%20during%20an%20internship%20meeting%2C%20saying%20good%20morning%20to%20a%20teacher%2C%20or%20offering%20to%20press%20the%20buttons%20for%20the%20other%20people%20in%20an%20elevator.%20Over%20time%2C%20these%20small%20tasks%20build%20confidence%20and%20create%20a%20leadership%20mindset.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229335b153-9613-4fca-9f51-bd91d9b5edde%5C%22%3EBe%20of%20value%20to%20others%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECreating%20value%20for%20others%20is%20the%20best%20way%20to%20make%20yourself%20successful.%20There%20are%20three%20types%20of%20value%3A%20material%2Ffinancial%2C%20emotional%2C%20and%20spiritual.%20Even%20affluent%20young%20people%20don't%20have%20much%20money%20but%20should%20learn%20to%20provide%20emotional%20or%20spiritual%20value%20to%20people%20around%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20way%20to%20put%20this%3A%20teach%20your%20teens%20to%20be%20more%20interested%20than%20interesting.%20Ask%20people%20about%20themselves.%20Recommend%20them%20a%20book.%20Make%20yourself%20someone%20others%20turn%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2236ec9cef-1921-4751-9b9b-2c099b5e885d%5C%22%3EExceed%20expectations%20on%20purpose%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20exceed%20expectations%2C%20people%20are%20thrilled%20%E2%80%94%20and%20they%20value%20you.%20It%20feels%20really%20nice%20to%20make%20someone%20else%20feel%20good%2C%20which%20is%20why%20young%20people%20should%20learn%20to%20exceed%20expectations%20on%20purpose.%20I%20call%20this%20intentionally%20creating%20lightning%20strikes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20kids%20are%20now%2028%20and%2030%2C%20but%20when%20they%20were%20younger%2C%20and%20someone%20visited%20our%20home%2C%20they%20would%20ask%20for%20the%20car%20keys%20and%20clean%20the%20visitor's%20car.%20It%20made%20the%20visitor%20happy%20and%20helped%20my%20kids%20stand%20out.%20Lightning%20strikes%20don't%20have%20to%20be%20this%20grand%20%E2%80%94%20they%20can%20be%20as%20simple%20as%20calling%20a%20grandparent%20to%20say%20hi%20or%20sending%20a%20handwritten%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226e423ece-dcad-4ee0-9fd1-01b81904cdea%5C%22%3EBuild%20good%20habits%20step%20by%20step%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20usually%20work%20with%20young%20people%20for%20a%20year%20at%20a%20time.%20It%20takes%20about%2060%20to%2090%20days%20to%20form%20a%20new%20habit%2C%20so%20over%20the%20course%20of%20the%20year%2C%20we%20focus%20on%20building%20four%20new%20high-performance%20habits.%20Adding%20one%20at%20a%20time%20doesn't%20feel%20overwhelming%2C%20but%20creating%20four%20new%20habits%20a%20year%20makes%20a%20difference%20in%20their%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStart%20small%3A%20Have%20your%20teen%20make%20their%20bed%20every%20day.%20Or%2C%20make%20it%20automatic%20that%20they%20clear%20the%20table%20after%20dinner.%20Over%20time%2C%20these%20changes%20add%20up%20for%20them%20and%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrue%20s