e%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Jeff%2C%2061%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20put%20together%20a%20plan%2C%20sold%20everything%20we%20owned%2C%20and%20hit%20the%20road%20with%20a%20couple%20of%20backpacks%20and%20a%20little%20suitcase.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20sold%20all%20their%20belongings%20and%20a%205-acre%20property%20in%20Oregon%20that%20included%20three%20outbuildings.%20They%20set%20a%C2%A0spending%20target%C2%A0of%20around%20%2440%2C000%20a%20year%2C%20which%20includes%20all%20travel%20expenses%20as%20well%20as%20general%20expenditures%20such%20as%20insurance%20and%20cellphone%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYear%20one%2C%20we%20went%20over%20budget%2C%26quot%3B%20Sandra%2C%2061%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BYear%20two%2C%20we'll%20be%20closer.%20We've%20learned%20some%20things%2C%20obviously%2C%20but%20it%20was%20less%20expensive%20than%20just%20living%20in%20a%20place%20somewhere%20in%20Oregon%20and%20not%20traveling.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226099%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20on%20her%20balcony%20on%20a%20cruise%20ship%20taking%20in%20the%20view%20of%20Glacier%20Bay%20National%20Park.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6818d4b8c6ad288d148000b9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224040%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESome%20retirees%20have%20struggled%20to%20budget%20for%20travel.%3Cp%3EBrycia%20James%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20decide%20which%20country%20to%20visit%20next%20based%20on%20affordability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20looked%20at%20Italy%20and%20went%2C%20'Hmm%2C%20yeah%2C%20not%20this%20year%20for%20sure%2C'%26quot%3B%20Jeff%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20so%20we%20put%20two%20months%20in%20Albania%20because%20the%20weather%20is%20similar%2C%20and%20it's%20a%20lot%20less%20expensive%20to%20rent%20a%20place%20for%20two%20months%20than%20it%20would%20be%20literally%20anywhere%20in%20Italy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJeff%20said%20they%20pl