20of%20just%20a%20capital%20provider%20for%20foreign%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20emphasis%20on%202030%20was%20really%20a%20statement%20to%20the%20world%20that%20we're%20going%20to%20do%20it%20ourselves%2C%26quot%3B%20Fink%20said%20about%20the%20country's%20sovereign%20wealth%20fund's%20plan%20to%20diversify%20and%20grow%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFraser%20said%20the%20next%20step%20for%20the%20country's%20capital%20markets%20would%20be%20to%20build%20a%20treasury%20function.%20Johnson%20boasted%20about%20her%20firm's%20new%20local%20private%20credit%20offering.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20could%20see%20the%20Kingdom%20being%20a%20top%2010%20economy%20in%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20Fink%20said%20of%20a%20country%20that%20produced%20%241.1%20trillion%20in%20GDP%20last%20year%20%E2%80%94%20less%20than%20half%20of%20what%20Canada%2C%20the%20world's%20tenth-largest%20economy%2C%20generated%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20optimism%20for%20the%20country's%20future%20did%20not%20take%20away%20from%20the%20general%20uncertainty%20many%20finance%20leaders%20have%20expressed%20about%20the%20immediate%20future%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20Trump%20administration's%20tariff%20policies%2C%20though%20the%20recent%20agreement%20with%20China%20has%20provided%20hope%20that%20the%20new%20global%20trade%20landscape%20will%20be%20clearer%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bigger%20fear%20expressed%20by%20Fink%20is%20not%20short-term%20volatility%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20really%20care%20about%20the%20next%2090%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20%E2%80%94%20but%20instead%20a%20continued%20reliance%20on%20public%20funding%20for%20long-term%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Bvitality%26quot%3B%20of%20any%20economy%2C%20he%20said%2C%20is%20measured%20by%20the%20amount%20of%20private%20capital%20flowing%20to%20investments%20that%20will%20take%20years%20to%20complete.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20those%20who%20have%20invested%20i