n%20spot%20an%20%26quot%3BAI-native%26quot%3B%20company%20from%20a%20mile%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20ChatGPT%20sounded%20the%20starting%20gun%20on%20the%20artificial%20intelligence%20revolution%2C%20Seseri%2C%20the%20cofounder%20and%20managing%20partner%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fglasswing-ventures-second-fund-158-million-betting-on-ai-tech-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGlasswing%20Ventures%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20was%20already%20writing%20the%20first%20checks%20to%20machine-learning%20startups%2C%20arguing%20that%20data-hungry%20algorithms%20would%20define%20the%20next%20era%20of%20software.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20current%20hype%20cycle%2C%20every%20tech%20startup%20is%20dedicating%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finvestors-pressuring-companies-to-get-serious-about-ai-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eresources%20to%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20the%20algorithms%20are%20doing%20the%20heavy%20lifting%20everywhere.%20Some%20teams%20grab%20an%20off-the-shelf%20model%2C%20wedge%20it%20into%20an%20otherwise%20ordinary%20software%20stack%2C%20and%20call%20it%20innovation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI-native%20companies%20follow%20a%20fundamentally%20different%20blueprint.%20Their%20core%20architecture%20is%20designed%20around%20machine%20intelligence%20from%20day%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFounders%20say%20that%20Seseri%20on%20a%20cap%20table%20has%20become%20code%20for%20%26quot%3Bthe%20real%20deal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPartnering%20with%20Glasswing%20instantly%20signals%20credibility%2C%26quot%3B%20Philippe%20Rival%2C%20whose%20risk%20management%20platform%20Enlaye%20received%20an%20investment%20from%20the%20firm%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BEveryone%20knows%20that%20if%20Glasswing%20is%20involved%2C%20it's%20a%20real%20AI-native%20company.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeseri%20has%20spent%20the%20better%20part%20of%20two%20decades%20investing%20and%20operating%20at%20the%20high-tech%20frontier.%20Before%20venture%20capital%2C%20Seseri%20was%20a%20senior%20manager%20in%20corporate%20development%20at%20Microsoft%2C%20where%20she%20led%20several%20acquisitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe's%20backed%20fast-rising%20enterprise-tech%20plays%2C%20including%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reprise.com%2Fresources%2Fblog%2Freprise-announces-62-million-series-b-funding-from-iconiq-growth-to-expand-product-led-growth-platform%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReprise%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20whose%20interactive%20demo%20platform%20drew%20a%20%2462%20million%20Series%20B%20in%202022%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fverusen.com%2Fnews%2Fsupply-chain-innovator-verusen-secures-25-million-in-series-b-funding%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVerusen%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20materials%20intelligence%20suite%20that%20raised%20%2425%20million%20that%20same%20year%3B%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.basetwo.ai%2Fannouncements%2Fbasetwo-raises-11-5m-series-a-to-transform-chemical-manufacturing-with-physics-ai-platform%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBasetwo%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20blends%20physics%20with%20AI%20to%20tune%20drug-%20and%20chemical-production%20lines%20and%20secured%20an%20%2411%20million%20Series%20A%20this%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%202018%2C%20the%20firm's%20assets%20have%20swelled%20to%20over%20%24270%20million%20across%20two%20funds.%20It's%20going%20back%20out%20for%20more%3B%20an%20SEC%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sec.gov%2FArchives%2Fedgar%2Fdata%2F2020922%2F000202092224000003%2FxslFormDX01%2Fprimary_doc.xml%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20filing%3C%2Fa%3E%20shows%20that%20Glasswing%20plans%20to%20raise%20a%20third%20fund.%20Seseri%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20fundraise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeseri%20has%20stayed%20ahead%20of%20the%20curve%20by%20being%20the%20first%20to%20identify%20founders%20poised%20to%20disrupt%20enterprises%20from%20logistics%20to%20Big%20Pharma.%20Glasswing%20said%20last%20year%20that%20it%20was%20the%20first%20institutional%20investor%20in%20all%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eof%20its%20portfolio%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFounders%20have%20no%20shortage%20of%20investors%20to%20choose%20from.%20Seseri%20said%20that%20when%20a%20founder%20has%20multiple%20term%20sheets%2C%20she%20wins%20deals%20because%20of%20her%20expertise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20is%20on%20the%20bleeding%20edge%20of%20everything%20with%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20Scott%20Matthews%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Verusen%2C%20said.%20Its%20cloud%20platform%20uses%20advanced%20data%20science%20and%20AI%20to%20clean%2C%20unify%2C%20and%20analyze%20the%20messy%20materials%20data%20in%20many%20manufacturers'%20enterprise%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFifteen%20years%20ago%2C%20Seseri%20was%20leading%20deals%20as%20a%20software%20investor%20at%20Fairhaven%20Capital%2C%20an%20early%20entrant%20in%20Boston's%20venture%20scene.%20One%20day%2C%20she%20waved%20Rick%20Grinnell%2C%20her%20mentor%20and%20one%20of%20the%20firm's%20founders%2C%20over%20to%20her%20desk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20had%20noticed%20something%20new%20about%20the%20companies%20she%20was%20meeting.%20With%20the%20increased%20availability%20of%20big%20data%20and%20ever-more%20powerful%20compute%2C%20founders%20were%20applying%20deep%20learning%20to%20tackle%20complex%20problems%20for%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20something%20happening%20and%20it's%20not%20big%20data%2C%26quot%3B%20Seseri%20told%20Grinnell.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20telling%20you%20something%20has%20changed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20nudged%20Seseri%20to%20dig%20deeper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20Seseri%20and%20Grinnell%20left%20Fairhaven%20to%20start%20Glasswing%2C%20centered%20on%20what%20she%20called%20a%20%26quot%3Bseismic%20shift%26quot%3B%20in%20technology.%20Forty%20percent%20of%20Fairhaven's%20limited%20partners%20signed%20on%20to%20back%20their%20initial%20fund.%20In%202022%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww