2_blank%5C%22%3Esoftware%20engineers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20eager%20to%20compete%20in%20a%20space%20without%20a%20staid%20market%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHarvey%20may%20have%20cracked%20the%20market%20open%2C%20but%20now%20it%20faces%20the%20classic%20innovator's%20dilemma%3A%20the%20very%20proof%20of%20concept%20it%20offered%20to%20the%20legal%20world%20is%20fueling%20a%20growing%20list%20of%20competitors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20legal-tech%20land%20grab%20is%20on.%20The%20question%20is%20whether%20Harvey%20can%20maintain%20its%20first-mover%20advantage%2C%20or%20if%20it's%20simply%20cleared%20the%20path%20for%20the%20next%20breakout.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d0f0f56d-ed74-4f83-b2d1-a112f93435a2%5C%22%3EWant%20in%3F%20Get%20in%20line.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20what%20fueled%20Harvey's%20ascent%20is%20its%20go-to-market%20strategy.%20Early%20on%2C%20the%20company%20bet%20that%20winning%20over%20the%20country's%20most%20elite%20law%20firms%20would%20create%20a%20ripple%20effect%20across%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20gated%20access%20to%20the%20product%20using%20a%20waitlist%2C%20allowing%20it%20to%20tightly%20tailor%20the%20tool%20to%20pilot%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20its%20Big%20Law%20wager%20appears%20to%20be%20paying%20off.%20Weinberg%20said%20lawyers%20at%20eight%20of%20the%2010%20highest-grossing%20firms%20in%20the%20nation%20are%20now%20using%20Harvey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20tells%20Business%20Insider%20it%20crossed%20%2470%20million%20in%20annual%20recurring%20revenue%20last%20quarter%2C%20putting%20it%20on%20pace%20to%20smash%20its%20goal%20of%20%24100%20million%20ARR%20for%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnce%20a%20subset%20of%20the%20market%20standardizes%20on%20a%20solution%2C%20it's%20kind%20of%20%3Cem%3Ethe%3C%2Fem%3E%20solution%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ilya%20Fushman%2C%20a%20venture%20capitalist%20who%20led%20Kleiner%20Perkins'%20investment%20in%20Harvey%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELeaning%20forward%20in%20a%20high-back%2C%20caramel-colored%20leather%20chair%2C%20Weinberg%20seemed%20unfazed%20by%20the%20growing%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHarvey's%20edge%2C%20he%20argued%2C%20lies%20in%20two%20places%20its%20rivals%20can't%20easily%20replicate%3A%20top-tier%20talent%20and%20a%20product%20strategy%20built%20on%20deep%20collaboration%20with%20its%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Harvey%20employees%20work%20during%20a%20product%20meeting.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681de58fc6ad288d14807950%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHarvey%20employees%20work%20during%20a%20product%20meeting.%3Cp%3EHarvey%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20260-person%20startup%20has%20lured%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoung-lawyers-choosing-work-startups-instead-big-law-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edozens%20of%20trained%20lawyers%3C%2Fa%3E%20off%20the%20gilded%20path%20to%20Big%20Law%20partnership%2C%20offering%20stock%20options%20and%20a%20shot%20at%20shaping%20the%20future%20of%20legal%20practice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20keep%20its%20edge%2C%20Harvey%20just%20made%20a%20key%20hire.%20Stripe%20veteran%20John%20Haddock%20has%20joined%20as%20chief%20business%20officer%20after%20a%20decade%20scaling%20one%20of%20Silicon%20Valley's%20most%20closely%20watched%20startups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaddock%20told%20BI%20he%20spoke%20to%20dozens%20of%20Harvey%20customers%20before%20accepting%20an%20offer.%20His%20decision%20boiled%20down%20to%20their%20love%20of%20the%20product.%20He%20called%20it%20Weinberg's%20%26quot%3BNo.%201%20maniacal%20focus.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20best%20thing%20we%20can%20do%20is%20stay%20focused%20on%3A%20are%20we%20building%20stuff%20that%20lawyers%20really%20need%20and%20need%20every%20day%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BEverything%20else%20takes%20care%20of%20itself.