0can%20turn%20workflows%20from%20custom%20projects%20into%20reusable%20building%20blocks%20%E2%80%94%20a%20sort%20of%20Lego%20kit%20it%20can%20adapt%20for%20each%20new%20client.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20bold%20strategy%2C%20but%20in%20a%20crowded%20field%2C%20Weinberg%20believes%20that%20winning%20won't%20come%20from%20better%20answers.%20It'll%20come%20from%20building%20a%20system%20that%20grows%20with%20the%20people%20asking%20the%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhat%20you%20want%20to%20do%20is%20build%20a%20solution%20that%20tracks%20the%20evolution%20of%20law%20over%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Amrussell%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Emrussell%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20Signal%20at%20%40MeliaRussell.01.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fharvey-legal-tech-startup-faces-growing-competition-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1747126802000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682230983fe8d39283659638%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fharvey-legal-tech-startup-faces-growing-competition-2025-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Three-year-old%20startup%20Harvey%20helped%20wake%20up%20the%20legal%20world%20to%20what%20AI%20could%20do%20for%20lawyers.%20A%20stampede%20of%20rivals%20followed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mrussell%40businessinsider.com%20(Melia%20Russell)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A55%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fharvey-legal-tech-startup-faces-growing-competition-2025-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22One%20of%20the%2