ed%20in%20bay%20leaf%20cultivation%20and%20basic%20processing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20area%20leading%20this%20transformation%20is%20the%20Hemtabad%20Block%2C%20now%20recognised%20as%20the%20top%20producer%20of%20the%20Bengal%20variety%20of%20bay%20leaves.%20According%20to%20Mahanta%2C%20one%20of%20the%20factors%20contributing%20to%20the%20crop%E2%80%99s%20popularity%20is%20its%20resilience.%20%E2%80%9CA%20bay%20leaf%20tree%20requires%20less%20water%20and%20low%20maintenance%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds%2C%20making%20it%20a%20sustainable%20option%20for%20many%20farmers%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20tree%20that%20keeps%20on%20giving%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20generations%2C%20farmers%20like%20Sukumar%20Barman%20in%20West%20Bengal%20relied%20on%20traditional%20crops%20like%20paddy.%20But%20the%20returns%20were%20modest%2C%20and%20the%20effort%20was%20relentless.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGrowing%20paddy%20on%20one%20bigha%20of%20land%20would%20fetch%20just%20Rs%2030%2C000%E2%80%9340%2C000%20a%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Barman.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20took%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20and%20labour%2C%20and%20getting%20the%20harvest%20to%20market%20on%20time%20was%20another%20challenge%20altogether.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%2C%20bay%20leaf%20cultivation%20has%20become%20a%20game-changer%20for%20his%20village.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20brought%20real%20economic%20development%20to%20our%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20about%20the%20spice.%20The%20tree%E2%80%99s%20twigs%20are%20ground%20into%20powders%2C%20its%20leaves%20are%20used%20as%20a%20natural%20colourant%2C%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20staple%20in