nstalling%20cool%20roof%20technology%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fem%3Econfirms%20Dipika.%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20has%20dramatically%20improved%20the%20lives%20of%20home-based%20workers.%20Previously%2C%20women%20doing%20sewing%20work%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20remain%20indoors%20between%201%20PM%20and%205%20PM%20due%20to%20excessive%20heat%2C%20forcing%20them%20to%20move%20their%20machines%20outside.%20Now%20they%20can%20work%20continuously%20inside%20their%20homes%2C%20extending%20their%20productive%20hours%20and%20increasing%20their%20income.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20we%20applied%20the%20solar%20reflective%20white%20paint%2C%20the%20difference%20in%20temperature%20indoors%20is%20remarkable.%20Before%2C%20it%20was%20unbearable%2C%20and%20I%20had%20to%20take%20breaks%20from%20my%20sewing%20to%20escape%20the%20heat.%20Now%2C%20with%20a%20cooler%20indoors%2C%20I%20can%20work%20longer%20hours%20comfortably%2C%20right%20here%20in%20my%20home.%20I%20am%20looking%20forward%20to%20applying%20the%20paint%20again%20next%20summer%20to%20maintain%20this%20comfortable%20environment%20for%20my%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%20Sangeeta%20Ben%20told%20The%20Better%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESaves%20energy%20costs%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECool%20roofs%20also%20reduce%20the%20use%20of%20mechanical%20air%20conditioning%2C%20resulting%20in%20significant%20savings%20in%20energy%20costs%2C%20considering%20the%20rising%20demand%20for%20power%20and%20the%20stress%20it%20exerts%20on%20the%20existing%20power%20infrastructure.%20Cool%20roofs%20are%20also%20an%20excellent%20solution%20for%20reducing%20the%20urban%20heat%20island%20effect%2C%20a%20phenomenon%20in%20